description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 3.1 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Room Air Conditioners that are effective as of October 1, 2013. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=roomac.pr_crit_room_ac
